A grimy tarromin is a herb that has not yet been cleaned to make a tarromin. Grimy tarromins may be grown from a tarromin seed with a Farming level of 19. It is dropped by certain NPCs. Cleaning a grimy tarromin requires a Herblore level of 11 and gives 5 Herblore experience. Clean tarromins are used to make Strength potions and Serum 207s with a Herblore level of 12 and a Herblore level of 15 respectively. Clean tarromins can also be used with swamp tar to create tarromin tar at level 39 Herblore.
